The article discusses how lower taxes on American businesses will lead to higher wages for American workers and increased production in the USA. President Donald J. Trump supports tax relief and cuts that will boost wages for hardworking Americans. The Unified Framework for Fixing Our Broken Tax Code, also supported by President Trump, aims to end the practice of companies offshoring profits and instead encourages them to invest in American workers. This framework will allow hardworking Americans to keep more of their money through tax cuts and relief.